text: Tomáš Havránek (born May 4, 1998) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for SK Horácká Slavia Třebíč of the Czech 1.liga. Havránek previously played for HC Kometa Brno of the Czech Extraliga and made his debut for the team during the 2015-16 Czech Extraliga season. He also had loan spells at Slavia Třebíč, HC Karlovy Vary and HC Dukla Jihlava before joining Slavia Třebíč permanently on May 12, 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:HC Dukla Jihlava players Category:SK Horácká Slavia Třebíč players Category:HC Karlovy Vary players Category:HC Kometa Brno players
